==Notes==
:A.{{Note|NoteA}} The 1717 weather event was made up of a series of snowstorms
:B.{{Note|NoteB}} Freezing rain
:C.{{Note|NoteC}} This storm was significant for its snow impact on [[Texas]]
:D.{{Note|NoteD}} While this nor'easter was not a major snow event, it was notable for the earliest snowfall ever recorded in [[Charleston, South Carolina]] and [[Savannah, Georgia]].
:E.{{Note|NoteE}} The 2006 Colorado Holiday Blizzards were made up of two different storms.
:F.{{Note|NoteF}} This event included multiple storms.
:G.{{Note|NoteG}} [[Hurricane Sandy]] caused a major snow event.

